pageProduct.name: SUP Shots Fit Energy 8x50ml Vials
pageProduct.description:
General Information

For that 'wake me up' kind of energy.

FUEL.IGNITE.TRAIN.
SUP is formulated to help fuel your physical and intellectual triumphs. We challenged our team to create a next level energy shot for you to get more out of your day. So, whether you're heading to the gym or into a meeting, make sure you're charged and on top of your game.

WHY SHOT SUP?
Drink your supplements on-the-go with our super shots. SUP is formulated with Bs vitamins and botanicals. SHOTSUP

Size: 8x50mL

KEY FEATURES

• An afternoon pick-me-up
• Support hair growth and thickness
• Hint of Caffeine
• Contains Vitamin Bs
• Shot your vitamin on-the-go

Warnings

The food is not a sole source of nutrition and should be consumed in conjunction with a nutritious diet and exercise program. Not suitable for children under 15 years of age or pregnant women. Should be used under medical or dietetic supervision. Do not use if tamper evidence seal is broken or missing. Store below 25?°C.

Ingredients

Water, Fresh Ginseng extract, Apple juice concentrate, Sweeteners (erythritol, steviol glycoside), Orange juice concentrate, Flavour (citric acid monohydrate), Stabiliser (HM pectin), Natural orange flavour, Blood orange juice, CoQ10, Natural apple flavour, Natural Pineapple flavour, Niacinamide (Vitamin B3), Caffeine, Germented grape extract, Cyanocobalamin (Vitamin B12), Pyridoxine hydrochloride (Vitamin B6), Thiamine mononitrate (Vitamin B1), Riboflavin (Vitamin B2).

Contains: CONTAINS CAFFEINE

Allergen Contains: Caffeine

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Egg| Gluten| Peanuts

Directions

SHOT 1 SUP (50mL) for that much needed energy hit.
Do not use if tamper evident seal is Broken or missing.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC
